constraints.name: simple_undirected_graph
constraints.description: 图是简单无向图，即任意一对顶点之间最多只有一条边

constraints.name: sequential_edge_removal
constraints.description: 依次移除给定的边，并在每次移除后报告图中剩余的桥的数量

constraints.name: valid_edges
constraints.description: 每条要移除的边必须是图中存在的边

constraints.name: no_duplicate_removal
constraints.description: 不会重复移除同一条边
